{"Title":"培根焗意面的做法","Primary":["螺丝粉100克","西红柿1/2个","洋葱1/2个","香菇3朵"],"Auxiliary":["橄榄油1汤匙","食盐1/2茶匙","番茄酱3汤匙","培根100克","白糖1茶匙","披萨草1克","罗勒叶1克","芝士片100克","水适量"],"Flavoring":[],"Setups":["1.准备好原料","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/177/03/1563427/n1563427_00038.jpg","2.烧水，滴几滴植物油，少许食盐","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/177/03/1563427/n1563427_92763.jpg","3.水开后下意面煮","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/177/03/1563427/n1563427_09321.jpg","4.煮熟后过一下凉水，滴少许橄榄油防沾","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/177/03/1563427/n1563427_83586.jpg","5.配料都切成小碎丁","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/177/03/1563427/n1563427_91170.jpg","6.平底锅下橄榄油","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/177/03/1563427/n1563427_45213.jpg","7.先下洋葱炒","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/177/03/1563427/n1563427_02008.jpg","8.炒出香味后倒培根碎","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/177/03/1563427/n1563427_37212.jpg","9.炒白后倒入西红柿和香菇，这时候加点食盐","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/177/03/1563427/n1563427_31130.jpg","10.西红柿出汁后加入番茄酱","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/177/03/1563427/n1563427_23977.jpg","11.加入白糖","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/177/03/1563427/n1563427_61892.jpg","12.加罗勒叶和披萨草","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/177/03/1563427/n1563427_20886.jpg","13.加适量开水","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/177/03/1563427/n1563427_36341.jpg","14.熬一会，汁收稍干","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/177/03/1563427/n1563427_66016.jpg","15.倒入意面","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/177/03/1563427/n1563427_23954.jpg","16.炒匀后倒入蒜碎","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/177/03/1563427/n1563427_18419.jpg","17.盛到烘焙碗里","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/177/03/1563427/n1563427_72196.jpg","18.铺上奶酪碎","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/177/03/1563427/n1563427_91661.jpg","19.烤箱中层，200度烤13分钟左右即可","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/177/03/1563427/n1563427_77454.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/177/03/1563427/n1563427_37707.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/177/03/1563427/n1563427_46431.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/177/03/1563427/n1563427_05838.jpg","烹饪技巧","　　可以随便放自己喜欢的菜。"]}